  <brief_title>Study To Evaluate The Efficacy And Safety Profile Of PF-06651600 And PF-06700841 In Subjects With Alopecia Areata</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multicenter Study With An Extension Period To Evaluate The Efficacy And Safety Profile Of PF-06651600 And PF-06700841 In Subjects With Moderate To Severe Alopecia Areata</official_title>
